---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Rank Labs">

<section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-sm text-cyan-300 font-mono mb-4">OUR STORY</div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About <span class="gradient-text">Rank Labs</span></h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg text-muted mb-8">
        Rank Labs was born from a simple observation: traditional SEO agencies are slow, expensive,
        and opaque. We asked a different question — what if SEO could be treated like a science?
        Methodical. Repeatable. Measurable.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">The Formula</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">
        Every site that enters the Rank Labs system goes through the same proven formula:
        crawl → analyze → optimize → create → repeat. AI handles the heavy lifting at every
        stage — crawling thousands of pages, identifying gaps, drafting content, and tracking
        rankings. You get the results without the agency overhead.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Why a Lab?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">
        Agencies rely on manual processes. Manual processes are slow, inconsistent, and expensive.
        A lab runs experiments at scale. Our AI runs the equivalent of a full SEO team's weekly
        output — every single day — for $599/month.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">
        You still get human oversight and final approval on everything. The AI does the work.
        You make the calls. That's the formula.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">The Tech Stack</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
        {[
          { label: 'Hosting', value: 'Cloudflare Pages (Global Edge)' },
          { label: 'Crawler', value: 'Custom AI Crawler Engine' },
          { label: 'Content', value: 'LLM-Powered Research & Writing' },
          { label: 'Monitoring', value: 'Prometheus + Grafana' },
          { label: 'Deployment', value: 'GitOps with Argo CD' },
          { label: 'Infrastructure', value: 'Kubernetes (k3s)' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="text-xs text-cyan-400 mb-1">{item.label}</div>
            <div class="text-sm">{item.value}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Based in Florida</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">
        Proudly operating from the Sunshine State. We serve businesses across the US —
        from local shops to national brands.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
